{"tid":1811860,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人，_ _","createTime":"2020-01-05T05:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T06:35:56.000Z","uid":206310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5120d6d2aa436f271a5701ed6bbb12116b290a","tid":1811860,"uid":206310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"最後兩個字係咩呢?<br />\n<br />\n由一開始講香港人加油，變香港人反抗，到呢家嘅香港人報仇，中間只係過咗四個月，幾乎係一個月升級一次。但係呢家每一次嗌口號嘅時候，嗌到香港人三個字，總會有人仲係嗌緊反抗，又或者有人仲係要load一陣先講到報仇。呢樣嘢反映出咗好多人心態上偏向於和理非，未突破武裝自衛呢個心理關口。<br />\n<br />\n使用適當武力制止蒙面暴徒呢個心理關口係難嘅。不過要知道，如果你冇任何攻擊能力，比你有再多嘅血量，都只你一個沙包。<br />\n<br />\n制止蒙面暴徒救人總會有人話係送頭、比人告襲擊；但係，當你淨係企喺度嘅時候都會告暴動而且判有罪嘅，其實打同唔打個分別只係有冇對蒙面暴徒造成損害，站在理性嘅角度上唔打先係一項不智嘅事。最起碼，都要練好個體能，被蒙面暴徒拎伸縮棍襲擊時有機會走得甩。<br />\n<br />\n利申：絕對唔鼓勵攻擊任何公職人員，蒙面暴徒絕對係講緊亂港嗰一班，市民應行使公民拘捕權處理嗰一班。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外行使公民拘捕權有其風險，請參考：<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/13820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F13820&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLfZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=b5f8ebd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/13820</a>"},{"pid":"bed6343523d859267bfdf54ce7ea34e5f19f4461","tid":1811860,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"潮文社：捉鬼是偽命題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811750</a>"},{"pid":"7ae42501df020df0438ba39cc5c91a07d0641bb5","tid":1811860,"uid":116054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"香港人，獨立"},{"pid":"874d201ff515c11cc8938befa0fa814ef527fd45","tid":1811860,"uid":8170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"香港人，團結。<br />\n正面得嚟多啲人肯叫。<br />\n得閒聽下十點叫，去到某啲粗口或者粗魯啲嘅就少啲人肯叫。"},{"pid":"7d50e2b3381880c9be156804ec7f9799eedb064c","tid":1811860,"uid":34811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"現實：香港人，返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fee226471ad2a15946cbfee8028eb27be1dd48e","tid":1811860,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7ae42501df020df0438ba39cc5c91a07d0641bb5","tid":1811860,"uid":116054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"香港人，獨立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"輸左都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014541f4057731b2aaf5fff4557ccf877f37639b","tid":1811860,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fee226471ad2a15946cbfee8028eb27be1dd48e","tid":1811860,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7ae42501df020df0438ba39cc5c91a07d0641bb5","tid":1811860,"uid":116054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"香港人，獨立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"輸左都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"輸咗 連香港人都唔會再有"},{"pid":"b90775a039f114e91a70fd4935af4b6d5fd040cf","tid":1811860,"uid":141763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，叫報仇個啲人味又係開路比後生上前線，自己係後面拍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c449b6da835d30dddaadf51361e4bf7a0a933e","tid":1811860,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fee226471ad2a15946cbfee8028eb27be1dd48e","tid":1811860,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7ae42501df020df0438ba39cc5c91a07d0641bb5","tid":1811860,"uid":116054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"香港人，獨立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"輸左都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:18:54.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會有<br />\n無人去做仲要連講都唔敢講<br />\n最叻就收埋係個心度<br />\n心裏獨立